document_data.name: Ithaqull
document_data.mainbody: '''Ithaqull''' was a very large [[beholder]] member of the [[Zhentarim]] in [[1358 DR]].
document_data.History: Ithaqull and many other beholders was with [[Manshoon]] when the wizard perceived the start of the [[Time of Troubles]] and whispered to Manshoon that the event would offer opportunities.
